<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>What’s included</h2>
<ul>
<li>Return flights</li>
<li>Return airport transfers - Train transfer for <a data-udi="umb://document/68449c4cf6264997983e6bb267a6d4ef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/68449c4cf6264997983e6bb267a6d4ef}" title="Passau to Vienna">Passau-Vienna tour</a> (unescorted) / Private taxi transfer for <a data-udi="umb://document/b5d61344574d447fb9ca5280d570ad84" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b5d61344574d447fb9ca5280d570ad84}" title="Vienna to Budapest">Vienna to Budapest tour</a></li>
<li>3 &amp; 4 star hotel accommodation for 8 days on bed/breakfast basis</li>
<li>Bike hire for 7 days (21 gear freewheel bike, with saddle bag)</li>
<li>Detailed route descriptions in English</li>
<li>Detailed map</li>
<li>Telephone assistance throughout the tour</li>
<li>Luggage service</li>
<li>3 Danube boat trips - for Passau to Vienna tour (bike transport included)</li>
<li>A return trip on the Pöstling mountain railway in Linz for Passau to Vienna tour</li>
<li>Train journey from Linz to Dornach - for Passau to Vienna tour</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 90%;">Bring your own bike (deduct £50 from package price but carriage supplement may apply). For guests taller than 1.90m or shorter than 1.60m, please notify us at time of booking. Credit card needed for a local security deposit for optional upgraded E-bike or bike accessories. <span id="id62f"><span id="id631" class="tab-panel"><span>Cost of a train ticket from Greifenstein to Vienna extra, approx. €5 per person.</span></span></span></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Optional Extras</h2>
<ul>
<li>Upgrade to eBike hire: Adults £84 / Child £42</li>
<li>Helmet approx. €32 (book locally, available in Passau and Vienna)</li>
<li>Half board upgrade 3-course evening meals, may be at a nearby restaurant </li>
<li>Extend your stay in Vienna or Budapest</li>
</ul>
